{"tid":2442617,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"木村光希接陸綜「千萬片酬」曝光！　媒體人爆料：中國出道當歌手","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T15:43:00.000Z","uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c95d1cbed5900b1231992fce9b168e0ba1801711","tid":2442617,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"2021年03月11日 19:26<br />\n<br />\n記者陳芊秀／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本星二代木村光希（Koki）在陸綜《創造營2021》登場，並擔任「特邀助力官」，讓參賽選手興奮破表。而她不只擔任助力官，還為節目主題曲寫英文歌詞，接陸綜的酬勞也曝光了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據日媒《女性SEVEN》報導，熟悉大陸影視圈的媒體人周來友透露，現在大陸娛樂景氣高速發展，吸引亞洲明星聚集，片酬也相當高，並爆料：「木村光希接《創造營2021》的酬勞，大概有1個節目300萬人民幣（日媒估算約4800萬日幣，人民幣換算台幣1321萬元）。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 木村光希接陸綜「千萬片酬」曝光！　媒體人爆料：中國出道當歌手 | ETtoday星光雲 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1936281#ixzz6oo5wD0fu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1936281%23ixzz6oo5wD0fu&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=5aa3724d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1936281#ixzz6oo5wD0fu</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"b1222767c4efb8c7d52c93facd80692ca71a9fbf","tid":2442617,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"木村拓哉實激死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221ae99f49a7a2d692ee0a773cc651eafe636c23","tid":2442617,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"人民幣太香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e700337765329c7338225fd642be3fdaff35311","tid":2442617,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:48:03.000Z","msg":"日星排住隊進軍中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa0fad17e8e09f5e56f8af9a01c40aa235be08b","tid":2442617,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT